184
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:09,878
A human life is an
ephemeral thing.

185
00:23:10,222 --> 00:23:12,747
It is a good idea to look
to the past from time to time.

186
00:23:13,258 --> 00:23:17,456
But perhaps my life is a trifle too long
to look back and dwell upon.

187
00:23:17,996 --> 00:23:18,830
And so,
I bid you farewell.

